#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:363
msgid "Gu! You are wounded! What is happening?!"
msgstr "¡Gu! ¡Estás herido! ¡¿Qué está pasando?!"

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:368
msgid "(dying) Orcs are attacking. I was not able to stop them."
msgstr "(muriendo) Los orcos están atacando. No pude detenerlos."

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:373
msgid ""
"We have been friends for a long time… but you can’t do anything for poor Gu "
"anymore."
msgstr ""
"Hemos sido amigos por mucho tiempo… pero no puedes hacer nada por el pobre "
"Gu ya."

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:378
msgid "Go to Zei. Find Csia."
msgstr "Ve a Zei. Encuentra a Csia."

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:383
msgid "If the orcs also betrayed us there, the king will need you."
msgstr "Si los orcos también nos traicionaron allí, el rey te necesitará."

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:388
msgid "Go, now! <i>dies</i>"
msgstr "¡Ve, ahora! <i>muere</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:399
msgid "Gu! No!"
msgstr "¡Gu! ¡No!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:404
msgid "Friends! To arms! We must free our land from the orcs!"
msgstr "¡Amigos! ¡A las armas! ¡Debemos liberar nuestra tierra de los orcos!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:409
msgid ""
"A few things will be a bit unusual in this campaign. Io can pick up and "
"equip items. You won't lose any gold if you have a negative income. However, "
"you won't get much gold at the beginning of scenarios beside what you had at "
"the end of the previous one. If you get stuck at the beginning of a "
"scenario, then it might be that you ended the previous one with too little "
"gold. You will be able to sell the objects you have gathered in shops in "
"exchange for gold, so don't forget to collect as many objects as you can."
msgstr ""
"Algunas cosas serán un poco inusuales en esta campaña. Io puede recoger y "
"equipar objetos. No perderás oro si tienes un ingreso negativo. Sin embargo, "
"no obtendrás mucho oro al inicio de los escenarios aparte de lo que tenías "
"al final del anterior. Si te atascas al inicio de un escenario, podría ser "
"que terminaste el anterior con poco oro. Podrás vender los objetos que has "
"recolectado en tiendas a cambio de oro, así que no olvides recolectar tantos "
"objetos como puedas."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:420
msgid ""
"It is not with my fists that I will fight against orcs. I need a weapon. \n"
"Let's grab this knife."
msgstr ""
"No es con mis puños que lucharé contra orcos. Necesito un arma. \n"
"Tomemos este cuchillo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:435
msgid "This is better. Now I can strike faster and harder."
msgstr "Esto es mejor. Ahora puedo golpear más rápido y fuerte."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:439
msgid ""
"If I find any, I could also use other weapons. \n"
"Clubs are like knifes, but more smashy and less stabby. Meanwhile, spears "
"are more powerful, but a bit slow."
msgstr ""
"Si encuentro algunos, podría usar otras armas. \n"
"Los garrotes son como cuchillos, pero más aplastantes y menos punzantes. "
"Mientras tanto, las lanzas son más poderosas, pero un poco lentas."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:453
msgid ""
"Too bad I am such a bad leader.\n"
"I am afraid I won't be able to manage more than 10 allies at once."
msgstr ""
"Qué mal que soy un líder tan malo.\n"
"Temo que no podré manejar más de 10 aliados a la vez."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:468
msgid "Poor Owepaup. He burnt with his house."
msgstr "Pobre Owepaup. Se quemó con su casa."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:472
msgid "Wait! I found something!"
msgstr "¡Espera! ¡Encontré algo!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:476
msgid "It looks like a half-burnt book. Might be useful."
msgstr "Parece un libro medio quemado. Podría ser útil."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:498
msgid "We have no time to kill all the orcs. We must hurry to Zei."
msgstr ""
"No tenemos tiempo para matar a todos los orcos. Debemos apresurarnos a Zei."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:509
msgid "Wait for us! We will try to kill some more orcs before leaving."
msgstr "¡Espérennos! Intentaremos matar algunos orcos más antes de irnos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:534
msgid "The orcs are all dead!"
msgstr "¡Los orcos están todos muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:538
msgid ""
"It looks like this one was going to leave with valuables stolen to our "
"friends. At least we were able to recover that."
msgstr ""
"Parece que este iba a irse con valiosos robados a nuestros amigos. Al menos "
"pudimos recuperar eso."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:542
msgid " I hope nothing happened in Zei. Let's go find out."
msgstr " Espero que nada haya pasado en Zei. Vamos a averiguarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:558
msgid ""
"We can't even kill a few orcs on our land. How could we imagine reaching Zei?"
msgstr ""
"No podemos ni matar a unos pocos orcos en nuestra tierra. ¿Cómo podríamos "
"imaginar llegar a Zei?"

#. [scenario], id=02_Helping_neighbors
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:5
msgid "Helping neighbors"
msgstr "Ayudando a vecinos"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:43
msgid "Move Io to the signpost at the south-west end of the map."
msgstr "Mueve a Io al poste de señal en el extremo suroeste del mapa."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:48
msgid "Defeat all enemy leaders"
msgstr "Derrota a todos los líderes enemigos"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:216
msgid "There might be a lot of orcs here too. We need to be careful."
msgstr "Podría haber muchos orcos aquí también. Necesitamos ser cuidadosos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:221
msgid "The bridge to Zei is south of here. Let's go."
msgstr "El puente a Zei está al sur de aquí. Vamos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:237
msgid "It smells like death in here."
msgstr "Huele a muerte aquí."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:256
msgid "So that's why."
msgstr "Por eso."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:273
msgid "I wonder if Hexe is still alive. Let's look inside."
msgstr "Me pregunto si Hexe sigue vivo. Miremos adentro."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:278
msgid "Alas, he was killed by an orc."
msgstr "Ay, fue asesinado por un orco."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:292
msgid "Anyway, I found a book upstairs. Maybe it contains information."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, encontré un libro arriba. Tal vez contenga información."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:314
msgid "It looks like Izu is still alive."
msgstr "Parece que Izu sigue vivo."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:320
msgid ""
"Hello $unit.name. I'm glad you're still alive too. I've had a rough day."
msgstr ""
"Hola $unit.name. Me alegra que sigas vivo también. He tenido un día difícil."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:326
msgid ""
"When I realized the orcs were attacking us, I tried to take refuge in my "
"cave but there was a little welcoming committee in there."
msgstr ""
"Cuando me di cuenta de que los orcos nos atacaban, intenté refugiarme en mi "
"cueva pero había un pequeño comité de bienvenida allí."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:332
msgid ""
"If you need some food for your trip to Zei and don't mind getting rid of the "
"few orcs remaining, you can take everything you'll find in my cave."
msgstr ""
"Si necesitas algo de comida para tu viaje a Zei y no te importa deshacerte "
"de los pocos orcos restantes, puedes tomar todo lo que encuentres en mi "
"cueva."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:347
msgid ""
"Thank you for getting rid of the orcs. If they chase farmers down to their "
"homes, you might have some trouble getting to Zei, so don't waste more time "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Gracias por deshacerte de los orcos. Si persiguen a los granjeros hasta sus "
"hogares, podrías tener problemas para llegar a Zei, así que no pierdas más "
"tiempo aquí."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:353
msgid "Here is a little present for you."
msgstr "Aquí tienes un pequeño regalo."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:360
msgid ""
"Take care of yourself and don't worry about me. I have enough food in my "
"cave to hold."
msgstr ""
"Cuídate y no te preocupes por mí. Tengo suficiente comida en mi cueva para "
"resistir."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:422
msgid "There is an odd-looking brick on that wall. Should I push it?"
msgstr "Hay un ladrillo de aspecto extraño en esa pared. ¿Debo empujarlo?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:424
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:500
msgid "Yes, let's try."
msgstr "Sí, intentémoslo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:468
msgid "That's clever."
msgstr "Eso es ingenioso."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:474
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:524
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:921
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:711
msgid "No, better not."
msgstr "No, mejor no."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:498
msgid "This wall looks fragile. I wonder what's behind. Shall I demolish it?"
msgstr "Esta pared parece frágil. Me pregunto qué hay detrás. ¿Debo demolerla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:518
msgid "Looks like there was a hidden room."
msgstr "Parece que había una habitación oculta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:550
msgid ""
"We must hurry. The bridge on the river is nearby. We have to get there "
"before something happens to it."
msgstr ""
"Debemos apresurarnos. El puente sobre el río está cerca. Tenemos que llegar "
"allí antes de que algo le pase."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:561
msgid "Wait for us! There are still people to help here."
msgstr "¡Espérennos! Aún hay gente a la que ayudar aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:619
msgid "The area is cleared."
msgstr "El área está despejada."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:623
msgid "I found the treasure of the orcish leader."
msgstr "Encontré el tesoro del líder orco."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:627
msgid "This might be useful. Let's move on and cross the bridge to Zei."
msgstr "Esto podría ser útil. Sigamos y crucemos el puente a Zei."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:641
msgid "The orcs are too strong for us. We won't be able to reach Zei..."
msgstr ""
"Los orcos son demasiado fuertes para nosotros. No podremos llegar a Zei..."

#. [scenario], id=03_Bridge_to_Zei
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:4
msgid "Bridge to Zei"
msgstr "Puente a Zei"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:44
msgid "Cross the bridge to Zei"
msgstr "Cruza el puente a Zei"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:54
msgid "Find another way to Zei"
msgstr "Encuentra otra forma de llegar a Zei"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:64
msgid "Find the entrance to the Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Encuentra la entrada a la Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:75
msgid "Kill all orcs"
msgstr "Mata a todos los orcos"

#. [side]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:323
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:401
msgid "Caged"
msgstr "Enjaulado"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:367
msgid "Finally. The bridge to Zei should be not far south."
msgstr "Finalmente. El puente a Zei no debería estar lejos al sur."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:371
msgid "Let's hurry to Zei before something happens."
msgstr "Apresurémonos a Zei antes de que algo pase."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:375
msgid ""
"If possible, it would be nice to kill any orcs we encounter. Our friends "
"have suffered enough already."
msgstr ""
"Si es posible, sería bueno matar a cualquier orco que encontremos. Nuestros "
"amigos han sufrido suficiente ya."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:389
msgid "Excuse me, do you happen to know what happened to the bridge?"
msgstr "Disculpe, ¿sabe qué pasó con el puente?"

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:393
msgid "Damn orcs happened."
msgstr "Los malditos orcos pasaron."

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:397
msgid "I know one is as bad as another but that’s the last straw."
msgstr ""
"Sé que uno es tan malo como otro pero eso es la gota que colma el vaso."

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:401
msgid ""
"They burnt the damn bridge down, then tried to cross it with their wagons "
"while it was still on fire!"
msgstr ""
"¡Quemaron el maldito puente, luego intentaron cruzarlo con sus carretas "
"mientras aún estaba en llamas!"

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:405
msgid ""
"They lost half-a-dozen orcs and sabotaged their own flight plan by "
"destroying the bridge."
msgstr ""
"Perdieron media docena de orcos y sabotearon su propio plan de huida al "
"destruir el puente."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:409
msgid "Do you know if there is another way to reach Zei?"
msgstr "¿Sabe si hay otra forma de llegar a Zei?"

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Now, the only way to reach Zei is to pass through the old crypts by taking "
"that road there. "
msgstr ""
"Ahora, la única forma de llegar a Zei es pasar por las antiguas criptas "
"tomando ese camino allí. "

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:417
msgid ""
"But don’t count on me coming with you. The way is probably full of orcs."
msgstr ""
"Pero no cuentes conmigo para ir contigo. El camino probablemente está lleno "
"de orcos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:441
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:548
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:614
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:662
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:710
msgid "There is a bat in this cage. Should I open it?"
msgstr "Hay un murciélago en esta jaula. ¿Debo abrirla?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:443
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:550
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:616
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:664
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:712
msgid "Yes, free it."
msgstr "Sí, libéralo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:461
msgid "It is free, but I don't think it was a safe idea."
msgstr "Está libre, pero no creo que fuera una idea segura."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:466
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:573
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:639
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:687
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:735
msgid "No, it's not a good idea. It could attack you."
msgstr "No, no es una buena idea. Podría atacarte."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:489
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:621
msgid "The staff of the statue looks like a lever. Should I try pulling it?"
msgstr "El bastón de la estatua parece una palanca. ¿Debo intentar jalarla?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:491
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:623
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:513
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:556
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:635
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:772
