#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:694
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:825
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1293
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:605
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:740
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:783
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:840
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:913
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\13_Miners_life.cfg:1200
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\13_Miners_life.cfg:1267
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\13_Miners_life.cfg:1311
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1340
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1367
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2829
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:458
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:483
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:689
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:706
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:796
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:821
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1031
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1048
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1138
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1163
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1208
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1275
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1342
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1607
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1629
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1924
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:936 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:958
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1000 .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1025
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:409
msgid "Yes, do it."
msgstr "Sí, hazlo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:537
msgid "It looks like it opened the entrance of a secret tunnel."
msgstr "Parece que abrió la entrada de un túnel secreto."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:542
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:639
msgid "No, it might be a trap."
msgstr "No, podría ser una trampa."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:560
msgid ""
"North: Arable Highlands\n"
"West: Crypt of the Sacred Blood\n"
"South: Zei"
msgstr ""
"Norte: Tierras Altas Arables\n"
"Oeste: Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada\n"
"Sur: Zei"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:580
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:507
msgid "South: Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Sur: Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:598
msgid "West: Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Oeste: Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:656
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:687
msgid "I found the entrance of the crypt."
msgstr "Encontré la entrada de la cripta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:660
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:691
msgid ""
"I'm a bit worried of what we might find inside, but we have no other choice "
"if we want to reach Zei. Let's enter the crypt but be careful everyone."
msgstr ""
"Estoy un poco preocupado por lo que podríamos encontrar adentro, pero no "
"tenemos otra opción si queremos llegar a Zei. Entremos a la cripta pero sean "
"cuidadosos todos."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:682
msgid ""
"I don't see any more orc around here. We can continue our journey knowing "
"that our friends will have a least a break."
msgstr ""
"No veo más orcos por aquí. Podemos continuar nuestro viaje sabiendo que "
"nuestros amigos tendrán al menos un respiro."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:718
msgid "Suddenly..."
msgstr "De repente..."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:725
msgid "What is that?! A walking skeleton! What is happening here?!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué es eso?! ¡Un esqueleto andante! ¡¿Qué está pasando aquí?!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:756
msgid "Alas..."
msgstr "Ay..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:760
msgid ""
"The bridge! It is destroyed! What happened there?! How will we be able to "
"rally Zei now?"
msgstr ""
"¡El puente! ¡Está destruido! ¡¿Qué pasó allí?! ¡¿Cómo podremos llegar a Zei "
"ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:773
msgid ""
"It will be too dangerous entering the crypt if someone is animating the "
"dead. We'd better find a way to repair the bridge"
msgstr ""
"Será demasiado peligroso entrar a la cripta si alguien está animando a los "
"muertos. Mejor encontramos una forma de reparar el puente"

#. [scenario], id=04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:4
msgid "Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:37
msgid "Reach the exit of the crypt"
msgstr "Alcanza la salida de la cripta"

#. [side], type=Deathblade
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:88
msgid "Skeletons"
msgstr "Esqueletos"

#. [side], type=Gargoyle
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:157
msgid "Gargoyles"
msgstr "Gárgolas"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:482
msgid "This skeleton we've seen up there is worrying."
msgstr "Este esqueleto que vimos arriba es preocupante."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:486
msgid ""
"I hope no one has had the idea to animate the dead that can be found in this "
"crypt."
msgstr ""
"Espero que nadie haya tenido la idea de animar a los muertos que se pueden "
"encontrar en esta cripta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:490
msgid "Anyway, we have no choice. We must cross this crypt to reach Zei. "
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, no tenemos opción. Debemos cruzar esta cripta para llegar a "
"Zei. "

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:511
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:633
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:814
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:692
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:823
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1017
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:911
msgid "There is a large wooden door. Should I try to open it?"
msgstr "Hay una gran puerta de madera. ¿Debo intentar abrirla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:531
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:654
msgid "Part of the wall fell when I opened the door."
msgstr "Parte de la pared cayó cuando abrí la puerta."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:536
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:712
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:800
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1038
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1312
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:623
msgid "Wait a bit. We'll have to open it but don't do it right now."
msgstr "Espera un poco. Tendremos que abrirla pero no lo hagas ahora."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:554
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:838
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1922
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:407
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it?"
msgstr "Hay una palanca en el piso. ¿Debo jalarla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:584
msgid "It has opened a portion of the wall."
msgstr "Ha abierto una porción de la pared."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:605
msgid "The portion of wall is closed back."
msgstr "La porción de pared se cerró de nuevo."

