#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1475
msgid ""
"Captain Soimaql told us to mount guard while the detachment is in the Hall "
"of Skulls. I am trying to distract myself by killing a few targets until "
"they come back."
msgstr ""
"El capitán Soimaql nos dijo que montáramos guardia mientras el destacamento "
"está en la Sala de las Calaveras. Intento distraerme matando algunos "
"objetivos hasta que regresen."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1490
msgid ""
"You look honest, so will I also be with you... The Ocks have plundered Oof's "
"stock and we don't have enough cereals left for our horses. "
msgstr ""
"Pareces honesto, así que yo también lo seré contigo... Los Ocks saquearon "
"las provisiones de Oof y no nos quedan suficientes cereales para nuestros "
"caballos."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1494
msgid ""
"We have no choice anymore... We are reduced to either let our animals die or "
"eat them. "
msgstr ""
"Ya no tenemos opción... Estamos reducidos a dejar que nuestros animales "
"mueran o comerlos."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1515
msgid ""
"You easily understand that it does not rejoice me at all, but I will have to "
"ask you for 30000 gold and, in exchange, I will let you leave with a strong "
"and brave horse."
msgstr ""
"Entiendes fácilmente que esto no me alegra en absoluto, pero tendré que "
"pedirte 30000 de oro y, a cambio, te dejaré ir con un caballo fuerte y "
"valiente."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1517
msgid "I'm sorry but we don't need a horse."
msgstr "Lo siento, pero no necesitamos un caballo."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1523
msgid "Here, take this"
msgstr "Aquí, toma esto"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1537
msgid "I'm sorry but you don't have enough gold."
msgstr "Lo siento, pero no tienes suficiente oro."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1578
msgid "Excuse me, but you look furious."
msgstr "Disculpa, pero pareces furioso."

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1582
msgid ""
"For Of's sake, we got our hands back on a worthless pile of wood, so what? "
"Has any of us seen the color of any gold coin since the beginning of this "
"chaos? "
msgstr ""
"Por el bien de Of, recuperamos un montón de madera sin valor, ¿y qué? "
"¿Alguno de nosotros ha visto el color de alguna moneda de oro desde el "
"inicio de este caos?"

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1586
msgid "Of course not! I'm fed up with spilling my blood for nothing."
msgstr "¡Por supuesto que no! Estoy harto de derramar mi sangre para nada."

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1605
msgid ""
"I gonna tell you... if you've 84250 gold for me, I follow you without "
"turning back and you'll be able to tell that Skepf works for you. What do "
"you think?"
msgstr ""
"Te voy a decir... si tienes 84250 de oro para mí, te sigo sin mirar atrás y "
"podrás decir que Skepf trabaja para ti. ¿Qué opinas?"

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1617
msgid "Who do you think I am?! I don't work for cheap!"
msgstr "¡¿Quién te crees que soy?! ¡No trabajo barato!"

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1638
msgid "I think I'll like working for you."
msgstr "Creo que me va a gustar trabajar para ti."

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1642
msgid "Deal! Skepf is your man!"
msgstr "¡Trato! ¡Skepf es tu hombre!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1646
msgid "You can now recruit dwarvish steelclads."
msgstr "Ahora puedes reincorporar guardias de acero enanos."

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1657
msgid "Well, well. "
msgstr "Bueno, bueno."

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1661
msgid "Do what you want, while WE slave away for that bloody kingdom! "
msgstr ""
"Hagan lo que quieran, mientras NOSOTROS nos esclavizamos para ese maldito "
"reino!"

#. [message], speaker=Skepf
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1665
msgid "Go rot in hell!"
msgstr "¡Vayan a pudrirse en el infierno!"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1695
msgid ""
"This door leads you to the shortest path to the desert. The Hall of Skulls "
"is down there, so be careful."
msgstr ""
"Esta puerta te lleva al camino más corto hacia el desierto. La Sala de las "
"Calaveras está allá abajo, así que ten cuidado."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1699
msgid ""
"It is some kind of old temple and, for a bit more than a week, it is "
"occupied by the dunefolk."
msgstr ""
"Es una especie de templo antiguo y, desde hace poco más de una semana, está "
"ocupado por los Barjanes."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1703
msgid ""
"A pikeman saw the dunefolk take a young girl inside during the battle: we "
"sent a regiment at her rescue, but no one came back. "
msgstr ""
"Un piquero vio a los Barjanes llevarse a una joven adentro durante la "
"batalla: enviamos un regimiento a rescatarla, pero nadie regresó."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1707
msgid "This must be Bta, my cousin. We have to go save her!"
msgstr "Esta debe ser Bta, mi prima. ¡Tenemos que ir a salvarla!"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1711
msgid ""
"Nothing could have happened to them: they were fighting mere dunefolks, "
"after all. I think they will appreciate your help."
msgstr ""
"Nada podría haberles pasado: después de todo, estaban luchando contra "
"simples Barjanes. Creo que agradecerán tu ayuda."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1733
msgid "Where are you going? We need to talk to Captain Soimaql."
msgstr "¿Adónde vas? Necesitamos hablar con el capitán Soimaql."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1739
msgid ""
"My friends, the next step of our mission is the Hall of Skulls and the "
"western Dunefolk village."
msgstr ""
"Mis amigos, el siguiente paso de nuestra misión es la Sala de las Calaveras "
"y la aldea Barján del oeste."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1748
msgid "Please don't forget that we need to save my cousin while we are there."
msgstr ""
"Por favor no olviden que necesitamos salvar a mi prima mientras estemos ahí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1754
msgid ""
"If possible, we should try to rescue the girl they kidnapped when we will be "
"there."
msgstr ""
"Si es posible, deberíamos intentar rescatar a la chica que secuestraron "
"cuando estemos allí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:1760
msgid ""
"Then we will hopefully be able to reach Idaamub's castle with no further "
"delay to bring our message to the king."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, con suerte, podremos llegar al castillo de Idaamub sin más demoras "
"para llevar nuestro mensaje al rey."

#. [scenario], id=40_Hall_of_Skulls
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:4
msgid "Hall of Skulls"
msgstr "Sala de las Calaveras"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:36
msgid "Exit the cave to the east"
msgstr "Sal de la cueva hacia el este"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:41
msgid "Get rid of all Dunefolk"
msgstr "Deshazte de todos los Barjanes"

#. [side], type=Spectre
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:179
msgid "Skulls"
msgstr "Calaveras"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:314
msgid "One more cave."
msgstr "Una cueva más."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:318
msgid ""
"Our main mission remains the same. We need to reach Idaamub's castle. To do "
"so, we will need to pass through Dunefolk territory."
msgstr ""
"Nuestra misión principal sigue siendo la misma. Necesitamos llegar al "
"castillo de Idaamub. Para hacerlo, tendremos que pasar por territorio Barján."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:322
msgid ""
"Dunefolk seem to have allied with Ocks, so we will most probably have to "
"fight against them. Captain Soimaql also asked us to capture the western "
"Dunefolk village."
msgstr ""
"Los Barjanes parecen haberse aliado con los Ocks, así que probablemente "
"tendremos que luchar contra ellos. El capitán Soimaql también nos pidió "
"capturar la aldea Barján del oeste."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:332
msgid "We also need to find my cousin, Bta, who was taken by the Dunefolk."
msgstr ""
"También necesitamos encontrar a mi prima Bta, que fue capturada por los "
"Barjanes."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:336
msgid ""
"I know you are worried about your cousin, but I don't think she at risk in "
"the hand of the Dunefolk. We will rescue her if we find her, but we won't "
"get out of our way to look for her."
msgstr ""
"Sé que estás preocupado por tu prima, pero no creo que esté en riesgo en "
"manos de los Barjanes. La rescataremos si la encontramos, pero no nos "
"desviaremos de nuestro camino para buscarla."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:342
msgid ""
"The Dunefolk also seem to have taken a young girl. We will rescue her if we "
"find her, but our mission should take priority. "
msgstr ""
"Los Barjanes también parecen haber capturado a una joven. La rescataremos si "
"la encontramos, pero nuestra misión debe tener prioridad."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:364
msgid ""
"There is a huge skull carved into the rock. There is a lever on the floor on "
"its left."
msgstr ""
"Hay un cráneo enorme tallado en la roca. Hay una palanca en el suelo a su "
"izquierda."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:384
msgid ""
"I think I found the patrol. It looks like they were ambushed by the Dunefolk "
"in the Hall."
msgstr ""
"Creo que encontré la patrulla. Parece que fueron emboscados por los Barjanes "
"en la sala."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:388
msgid ""
"Be careful everyone. We know they are here, so please try not to end like "
"those poor legionaries."
msgstr ""
"Tengan cuidado todos. Sabemos que están aquí, así que intenten no terminar "
"como esos pobres legionarios."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:423
msgid "The skull opened its mouth. There seem to be a room behind."
msgstr "El cráneo abrió la boca. Parece que hay una habitación detrás."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:433
msgid "I assume it must be the Hall of Skull."
msgstr "Supongo que esta debe ser la Sala de las Calaveras."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:437
msgid "We have to explore it. The Dunefolk might have taken Bta there."
msgstr "Tenemos que explorarla. Los Barjanes podrían haber llevado a Bta ahí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:443
msgid ""
"I assume it must be the Hall of Skulls. The Dunefolk might have taken the "
"girl there."
msgstr ""
"Supongo que esta debe ser la Sala de las Calaveras. Los Barjanes podrían "
"haber llevado a la chica ahí."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:468
msgid "Undead?!"
msgstr "¡¿No-muertos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:472
msgid ""
"Isut's undead already had surrounded the fortress? It was closer from "
"falling than we thought."
msgstr ""
"¿Los no-muertos de Isut ya habían rodeado la fortaleza? Estaba más cerca de "
"caer de lo que pensábamos."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:476
msgid "Don't worry. Those have always been there."
msgstr "No se preocupen. Esos siempre han estado ahí."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:480
msgid ""
"The Hall of Skulls is a necropolis, so such a phenomenon tends to happen."
msgstr ""
"La Sala de las Calaveras es una necrópolis, así que este tipo de fenómeno "
"suele ocurrir."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:499
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:536
msgid "There is a huge sarcophagus. Should I have a look at what is inside?"
msgstr "Hay un sarcófago enorme. ¿Debería mirar qué hay dentro?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:501
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:538
msgid "Yes, but carefully."
msgstr "Sí, pero con cuidado."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:509
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:546
msgid "There was a treasure in the sarcophagus."
msgstr "Había un tesoro en el sarcófago."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:514
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:551
msgid "No, we are no tomb raider."
msgstr "No, no somos saqueadores de tumbas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:574
msgid "Here is the exit. Let's continue to the Dunefolk village."
msgstr "Aquí está la salida. Sigamos hacia la aldea Barján."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:584
msgid "We cannot leave yet. We have not looked everywhere for Bta."
msgstr "No podemos irnos todavía. No hemos buscado en todos lados a Bta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:588
msgid ""
"I am sorry Ubidaiubua, but our mission is too important, we cannot waste "
"more time in this cave."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento Ubidaiubua, pero nuestra misión es demasiado importante, no "
"podemos perder más tiempo en esta cueva."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:592
msgid "<i>visibly angry</i> I will remember that."
msgstr "<i>visiblemente enojado</i> Voy a recordar eso."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:606
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:778
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:829
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the Dunefolk here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Todavía estamos luchando contra los Barjanes aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:628
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:849
msgid ""
"I don't see any other Dunefolk around here. He must have been the last one."
msgstr "No veo más Barjanes por aquí. Debe haber sido el último."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:638
msgid "And still no sign of Bta. I wonder where she might be."
msgstr "Y todavía ninguna señal de Bta. Me pregunto dónde podría estar."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:642
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:656
msgid ""
"They probably took her to the village. I am sure we will find her there."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente la llevaron a la aldea. Estoy seguro de que la encontraremos "
"allí."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:646
msgid "I hope so."
msgstr "Eso espero."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:652
msgid "And still no sign of the girl. I wonder where she might be."
msgstr "Y todavía ninguna señal de la chica. Me pregunto dónde podría estar."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:660
msgid "At least I hope so."
msgstr "Al menos eso espero."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:666
msgid "Now let's continue to the Dunefolk village."
msgstr "Ahora sigamos hacia la aldea Barján."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\40_Hall_of_Skulls.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Dunefolk are indeed as good fighters as blacksmith. I don't think we will be "
"able to defeat them."
msgstr ""
"Los Barjanes son tan buenos luchadores como herreros. No creo que podamos "
"derrotarlos."

#. [scenario], id=41_Sand_River
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:4
msgid "Sand River"
msgstr "Río de Arena"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:33
msgid "Progress to the east"
msgstr "Avanza hacia el este"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:474
msgid ""
"I had heard that the desert was warm, but I have to admit I was not "
"excepting something that harsh. How can people even live here?"
msgstr ""
"Había oído que el desierto era cálido, pero debo admitir que no esperaba "
"algo tan duro. ¿Cómo puede la gente vivir aquí?"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:481
msgid ""
"Hardly. I heard they mostly live during the night and dress in light white "
"clothes."
msgstr ""
"Apenas. Escuché que viven mayormente de noche y visten ropa blanca ligera."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:485
msgid "It seems there is still some water around here."
msgstr "Parece que todavía hay algo de agua por aquí."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:489
msgid ""
"The water comes from the mountain. I read that they cultivate the soil that "
"is close to the river."
msgstr ""
"El agua viene de la montaña. Leí que cultivan el suelo que está cerca del "
"río."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:493
msgid ""
"It overflows once a year, bringing nutrients from the mountains and "
"depositing it on the fields. I also heard that the river is full of "
"ferocious animals though."
msgstr ""
"Se desborda una vez al año, trayendo nutrientes de las montañas y "
"depositándolos en los campos. También escuché que el río está lleno de "
"animales feroces."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:503
msgid ""
"Anyway, we are not here to settle but to defeat the Dunefolk and find Bta. "
"Let's go."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, no estamos aquí para establecernos sino para derrotar a los "
"Barjanes y encontrar a Bta. Vamos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:509
msgid ""
"Anyway, we are not here to settle but to defeat the Dunefolk and find the "
"girl. Let's go."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, no estamos aquí para establecernos sino para derrotar a los "
"Barjanes y encontrar a la chica. Vamos."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:526
msgid "That's one weird looking lizard."
msgstr "Ese es un lagarto de aspecto extraño."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:535
msgid "Is this one of those famous river lizards?"
msgstr "¿Es este uno de esos famosos lagartos de río?"

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:539
msgid "Yes, but be careful, they are carnivorous."
msgstr "Sí, pero ten cuidado, son carnívoros."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:543
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "Oh."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:563
msgid "Hello. Who are you?"
msgstr "Hola. ¿Quién eres?"

#. [message], speaker=Rboekmocqu
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:567
msgid ""
"I'm Rboekmocqu. One eternity ago, I fought side by side with da 10th Legion "
"during da Battle of da Plains. "
msgstr ""
"Soy Rboekmocqu. Hace una eternidad luché codo a codo con la 10ª Legión "
"durante la Batalla de las Llanuras."

#. [message], speaker=Rboekmocqu
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:571
msgid ""
"Nowadays, I don't trust anyone, be it king, Legion, Dunefolk, even Traveler. "
"Gold's da only thing I trust."
msgstr ""
"Hoy en día no confío en nadie, sea rey, Legión, Barján o incluso viajero. El "
"oro es lo único en lo que confío."

#. [message], speaker=Rboekmocqu
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:590
msgid ""
"If ya're interested, I could fight fo ya. But if ya want me t'fight fo ya, "
"ya havta EARN ma trust (91150 gold)."
msgstr ""
"Si te interesa, podría luchar por ti. Pero si quieres que luche por ti, "
"tienes que GANAR mi confianza (91150 de oro)."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:592
msgid "Is this enough a proof of trust?"
msgstr "¿Es esto suficiente prueba de confianza?"

#. [message], speaker=Rboekmocqu
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:602
msgid "No, I still don't trust you (you do not have enough gold)."
msgstr "No, todavía no confío en ti (no tienes suficiente oro)."

#. [message], speaker=Rboekmocqu
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:623
msgid "Deal! "
msgstr "¡Trato!"

#. [message], speaker=Rboekmocqu
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:627
msgid ""
"I'll fight fo ya as long as I can but don't expect me t'bow before the "
"kingdom's big shots. Da only authority I respect's mine."
msgstr ""
"Lucharé por ti mientras pueda, pero no esperes que me incline ante los "
"grandes del reino. La única autoridad que respeto es la mía."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:631
msgid "You can now recruit dwarvish pathfinders."
msgstr "Ahora puedes reincorporar rastreadores enanos."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:638
msgid "Sorry, trust can't be bought."
msgstr "Lo siento, la confianza no se compra."

#. [message], speaker=Rboekmocqu
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:642
msgid "As ya wish! But pray da other side don't make me a better offer."
msgstr ""
"¡Como quieras! Pero reza para que el otro lado no me haga una mejor oferta."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:675
msgid ""
"North: Oof's fortress\n"
"South: Fire Cliffs"
msgstr ""
"Norte: Fortaleza de Oof\n"
"Sur: Acantilados de Fuego"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:694
msgid ""
"It looks like the Dunefolk are blocking the bridge. We will have to defeat "
"them to continue."
msgstr ""
"Parece que los Barjanes están bloqueando el puente. Tendremos que "
"derrotarlos para continuar."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:714
msgid "There is an elevator here."
msgstr "Hay un elevador aquí."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:736
msgid ""
"I don't see any path going further. I think we will have to take the "
"elevator."
msgstr ""
"No veo ningún camino que continúe. Creo que tendremos que tomar el elevador."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:750
msgid "Let me have a look at it before we all die falling from up there."
msgstr ""
"Déjenme echarle un vistazo antes de que todos muramos cayendo desde allá "
"arriba."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:755
msgid "I hate to admit that, but that's a nice piece of machinery..."
msgstr "Odio admitirlo, pero es una buena pieza de maquinaria..."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:759
msgid "You won't admit that it is better than dwarvish ones, will you?"
msgstr "No vas a admitir que es mejor que las enanas, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:784
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the animals here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Todavía estamos luchando contra los animales aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:798
msgid "How many Dunefolk are there?"
msgstr "¿Cuántos Barjanes hay?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:838
msgid "You were eaten by a Dreadscale."
msgstr "Fuiste devorado por un Lagarto del Terror."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\41_Sand_River.cfg:844
msgid ""
"As if fighting Dunefolk was not enough, now we have to fight wild animals on "
"top of that. I don't see how we could progress further."
msgstr ""
"Como si luchar contra los Barjanes no fuera suficiente, ahora también "
"tenemos que luchar contra animales salvajes. No veo cómo podríamos avanzar "
"más."

#. [scenario], id=42_Desert_Bridges
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:4
msgid "Desert Bridges"
msgstr "Puentes del Desierto"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:45
msgid "Find and subdue the Dunefolk western village"
msgstr "Encuentra y somete la aldea Barján del oeste"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:50
msgid "Get rid of all aggressive Dunefolk"
msgstr "Deshazte de todos los Barjanes agresivos"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:674
msgid ""
"Looks like we have a little welcome committee up there. It reminds me of "
"that time in the mine."
msgstr ""
"Parece que tenemos un pequeño comité de bienvenida allá arriba. Me recuerda "
"a aquella vez en la mina."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:678
msgid "At least, it must mean that we are getting close to the village."
msgstr "Al menos debe significar que nos estamos acercando a la aldea."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Our mission is to subdue it and then to continue our journey to Idaamub's "
"castle. Let's go."
msgstr ""
"Nuestra misión es someterla y luego continuar nuestro viaje al castillo de "
"Idaamub. Vamos."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:686
msgid "Don't forget that we also need to find my cousin."
msgstr "No olviden que también necesitamos encontrar a mi prima."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:701
msgid ""
"North: Fire Cliffs\n"
"East: Of's Fortress"
msgstr ""
"Norte: Acantilados de Fuego\n"
"Este: Fortaleza de Of"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:720
msgid ""
"North: Of's Fortress\n"
"South-East: Fire Cliffs, Idaamub's Castle"
msgstr ""
"Norte: Fortaleza de Of\n"
"Sureste: Acantilados de Fuego, Castillo de Idaamub"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:739
msgid "What's that? It looks like there is someone on that Wyvern."
msgstr "¿Qué es eso? Parece que hay alguien sobre ese Wyvern."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:743
msgid ""
"I heard that some of the Dunefolk are brave, or mad, enough to try to tame "
"Wyverns. It looks like this one succeeded."
msgstr ""
"Escuché que algunos Barjanes son lo suficientemente valientes, o locos, para "
"intentar domar Wyverns. Parece que este lo logró."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:762
msgid "This must be the village. Now let's find the entrance."
msgstr "Esta debe ser la aldea. Ahora busquemos la entrada."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:783
msgid "Here is the entrance."
msgstr "Aquí está la entrada."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:787
msgid ""
"This is weird, the portal is open, there is no one guarding it and I see no "
"one on the wall."
msgstr ""
"Esto es extraño, el portal está abierto, no hay nadie custodiando y no veo a "
"nadie en la muralla."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:791
msgid ""
"Let's hope it is because they had sent every soldier out to stop us from "
"arriving to the village."
msgstr ""
"Esperemos que sea porque enviaron a todos los soldados a detenernos antes de "
"que llegáramos a la aldea."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:813
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:853
msgid "Let's enter the village."
msgstr "Entremos a la aldea."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:817
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:857
msgid "I hope it is not a trap."
msgstr "Espero que no sea una trampa."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\42_Desert_Bridges.cfg:873
msgid ""
"Dunefolk are indeed as good fighters as blacksmith. I don't think we will be "
"able to reach the village."
msgstr ""
"Los Barjanes son tan buenos luchadores como herreros. No creo que podamos "
"llegar a la aldea."

#. [scenario], id=43_Western_Village
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:4
msgid "Western Village"
msgstr "Aldea del Oeste"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:25
msgid "Find and subdue the Dunefolk western village's leader"
msgstr "Encuentra y somete al líder de la aldea Barjanes del oeste"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:35
msgid "Leave the village"
msgstr "Sal de la aldea"

#. [note]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:51
msgid ""
"<b>This is currently the last scenario. It is advised not to sell items in "
"it as you will have to replay the scenario when the next chapter will be out."
"</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Este es actualmente el último escenario. Se recomienda no vender objetos "
"aquí porque tendrás que volver a jugar el escenario cuando salga el próximo "
"capítulo.</b>"

#. [side]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:141
msgid "Fanatics"
msgstr "Fanáticos"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:166
msgid "They are bowing before us. They do not seem to want to attack us."
msgstr "Están inclinándose ante nosotros. No parecen querer atacarnos."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:170
msgid "Be careful, they could be faking it."
msgstr "Tengan cuidado, podrían estar fingiendo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:174
msgid ""
"Anyway, we need to find the leader of the village and have him to surrender. "
"Then we will go to Idaamub's castle."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, necesitamos encontrar al líder de la aldea y hacer que se "
"rinda. Luego iremos al castillo de Idaamub."

#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:178
msgid ""
"Don't forget that we also need to find my cousin. I am sure she must be "
"there."
msgstr ""
"No olviden que también necesitamos encontrar a mi prima. Estoy seguro de que "
"debe estar ahí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:182
msgid ""
"I hope we won't have to fight here. It would be difficult to fight against "
"the dunefolk inside their own village."
msgstr ""
"Espero que no tengamos que luchar aquí. Sería difícil luchar contra los "
"Barjanes dentro de su propia aldea."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:202
msgid "Those guys don't look friendly."
msgstr "Esos tipos no parecen amigables."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:236
msgid "I'm Faiq, Paragon of the Western Village."
msgstr "Soy Faiq, Paragon de la Aldea del Oeste."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:247
msgid "Recall your men and surrender!"
msgstr "¡Reincorpora a tus hombres y ríndete!"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:251
msgid "Peace! We are all victims of these horrible Ocks!"
msgstr "¡Paz! ¡Todos somos víctimas de estos horribles Ocks!"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:259
msgid "They have been hunting us down for centuries to eradicate us."
msgstr "Nos han estado cazando durante siglos para erradicarnos."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:270
msgid "Why are you siding with the Ocks?"
msgstr "¿Por qué se están aliando con los Ocks?"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:274
msgid ""
"When they reappeared, our generation of warriors had just hatched. It was no "
"match against the old hexes the Ocks were using. "
msgstr ""
"Cuando reaparecieron, nuestra generación de guerreros acababa de nacer. No "
"éramos rivales para los viejos hechizos que usaban los Ocks."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:278
msgid ""
"To survive we concluded an... ill-advised alliance. We would like to redeem "
"ourselves. "
msgstr ""
"Para sobrevivir llegamos a una... alianza poco aconsejable. Nos gustaría "
"redimirnos."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:282
msgid "As a proof of good intentions, I offer you a barter."
msgstr "Como prueba de buenas intenciones, les ofrezco un trueque."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:293
msgid "Tell us what the Ock's plan is."
msgstr "Dinos cuál es el plan de los Ocks."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:297
msgid ""
"The Ocks want to seize hold of a secret room they intend to find in "
"Idaamub's castle."
msgstr ""
"Los Ocks quieren apoderarse de una habitación secreta que pretenden "
"encontrar en el castillo de Idaamub."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:301
msgid "You need to be quick if you want to prevent them from doing so."
msgstr "Necesitan ser rápidos si quieren impedírselo."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter6\43_Western_Village.cfg:315
msgid "Trade."
msgstr "Comerciar."

#. [message], speaker=trader
